commit.message:
pyproject.toml: update mypy to recent version

Also update the scripts affected by the newer mypy.
poetry.lock: update dependencies

.readthedocs.yml: fix rtd build

This time the official recommendation used:
https://docs.readthedocs.io/en/stable/build-customization.html#install-dependencies-with-poetry
doc: add doc.patch to fix typing.TYPE_CHECKING blocks for sphinx
doc: update werkzeug mapping
Makefile: add doc-preview target

doc: fix documentation in api.rst

Add the now-exported RequestMatcher class.
doc: add howto and example for log querying

httpserver: add methods to query log

New methods added to query log for the given matcher.

Fixes #293
shell.nix: use poetry-core instead of poetry
